(66, 'Tele Caller Expert', 'tele-caller-expert', 4, 1, 3, 2, NULL, '04 December, 2025', 'Nigeria', '<p>AIMS Education is a dynamic and growing organization dedicated to assisting students in navigating their educational journey. We provide comprehensive consultancy services to guide students towards their academic and career goals. As a Tele Caller Expert at AIMS Education, you will play a crucial role in expanding our reach and connecting with potential clients.</p><p><strong><br></strong></p><p><strong>Required Skills &amp; Expertise:</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Marketing</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Sales Marketing</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Salesman</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Talesales</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Telemarketing</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Telemarketing and sales</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Telesales Service</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Workplace</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Work at office</li></ul><p><br></p><p></p><p><strong>Experience</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>1 to 3 years</li><li>The applicants should have experience in the following business area(s): Immigration and Education Consultancy Service, Direct Selling/Marketing Service Company, Call Center</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Additional Requirements</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Age 18 to 40 years</li></ul><p></p>', NULL, '<p>Your primary responsibilities will include:</p><p></p><ul><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Proven experience in telemarketing or a related field.</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Ability to articulate the value of our services to potential clients.</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Goal-oriented mindset with a track record of meeting targets.</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Familiarity with the education sector is a plus.</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Conducting outbound calls to prospective students and their families.</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Explaining our consultancy services and addressing inquiries.</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Building and maintaining strong relationships with clients.</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Meeting weekly and monthly targets for lead generation.</li></ul><p></p><p><br></p>', '<p></p><ul><li>Higher Secondary, Bachelor/Honors</li></ul><p></p>', 'Tele Caller Expert', '1', 'AIMS Education', 'Hive Mall, 2nd Floor, 117 T.F. Kuboye Road, Maroko, Lekki, Lagos, 106104, Nigeria', 'https://aimseducation.co.uk', 0, 1, '2025-07-16 03:20:37', '2025-07-21 12:17:37'),
(67, 'Digital Marketing Executive', 'digital-marketing-executive', 5, 1, 3, 1, NULL, '05 December, 2025', 'Kochi, India', '<p>Are you passionate about fostering diversity, supporting education and connecting with talented individuals from around the world? We are excited to announce job opening for Digital Marketing Executive.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>The applicants should have experience in the following business area(s):</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Consulting Firms, Immigration/Visa Processing</li><li>Additional Requirements: Age 25 to 35 years</li></ul><p></p>', NULL, '<p></p><ul><li>Plans and executes all web, SEO/SEM/SMM, database marketing, email marketing, social media marketing, google AdSense, media buying and display advertising campaigns. Designs, builds and maintains our social media presence.</li><li>Graphic Designing, Motion Graphics, ex: static, dynamic·</li><li>&nbsp;Production ex; Scriptwriting, shooting, post-production·</li><li>Content writing (in English)· Data driven digital marketing ability.</li><li>Measures and reports the performance of all digital marketing campaigns and assesses against goals (ROI and KPIs).</li><li>Identifies trends and insights and optimizes spend and performance based on the insights.</li><li>Brainstorms new and creative growth strategies through digital marketing.</li><li>Plans, executes and measures experiments and conversion tests.</li><li>Collaborates with internal teams to create landing pages and optimize the user experience.</li><li>Utilizes strong analytical ability to evaluate end-to-end customer experience across multiple channels and customer touchpoints.</li><li>Identifies critical conversion points and drop-off points and optimizes user funnels.</li><li>Collaborates with agencies and other vendor partners.</li><li>Evaluates emerging technologies.</li><li>Provides thought leadership and perspective for adoption where appropriate.</li></ul><p></p>', '<p></p><ul><li>Bachelor/Honors</li></ul><p></p>', 'Digital Marketing Executive', '1', 'AIMS Education', 'Unit No. 3A, 3rd Floor, KG Oxford Business Center, Sreekandath Road, Ravipuram, Kochi, Ernakulam District, Kerala 682016', 'https://aimseducation.co.uk', 1, 1, '2025-07-16 03:27:03', '2025-07-21 12:18:02'),
(68, 'Graphic Designer', 'graphics-designer-video-editor-india', 3, 1, 3, 1, NULL, '05 December, 2025', 'Calicut, India', '<p>AIMS Education India is a leading student consultancy firm dedicated to helping students achieve their academic and career goals. We provide comprehensive guidance on educational opportunities, application processes, and career planning. Our dynamic team is passionate about making a positive impact on the lives of students.</p><p>We’re Hiring: <strong>Graphic Designer</strong></p><p>AIMS Education, a leading study abroad consultancy, is expanding in Calicut, and we’re looking for a creative and skilled Graphic Designer to join our team! If you have a passion for design and want to grow in a dynamic environment, this is your opportunity!</p><p><strong>☛Job Description:</strong></p><p>We are seeking a talented and creative Graphics Designer and Video Editor to join our team. The ideal candidate will have a strong eye for design, excellent video editing skills, and a passion for creating engaging visual content. This role involves working closely with our marketing and content teams to produce high-quality graphics and videos that communicate our brand’s message effectively.</p><p><strong><br></strong></p><p><strong>How to Apply?</strong></p><p>Interested candidates are invited to submit their CV, a cover letter</p>', '<p></p><ul><li>&nbsp;Competitive salary</li><li>Career growth opportunities</li><li>Work with a creative and friendly team</li><li>Exciting projects and learning opportunities</li></ul><p></p>', '<p></p><ul><li>Design graphics for social media, websites, and marketing materials</li><li>Edit videos and create motion graphics for promotional content</li><li>Develop branding materials like brochures, posters, and ads</li><li>Enhance images through retouching and color correction</li><li>Work with the marketing team to maintain brand consistency</li><li>Skills &amp; Requirements:</li><li>Minimum 1 year of experience in graphic design</li><li>Proficiency in Adobe Photoshop &amp; Illustrator</li><li>Basic knowledge of video editing &amp; 2D animation</li><li>Creativity and a good sense of color, layout, and typography</li><li>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment and meet deadlines</li></ul><p></p>', NULL, 'Graphic Designer', '1', 'AIMS Education', 'First Floor, City corner complex, West Nadakkave, Vandipetta, Bilathikkulam, Kozhikode, Kerala 673011, India', 'https://aimseducation.co.uk', 0, 1, '2025-07-16 03:33:24', '2025-07-21 12:18:23'),
(69, 'International Student Counsellor', 'student-counsellor-india', 1, 1, 3, 2, NULL, '29 December, 2025', 'Calicut, India', '<p>AIMS Education is a leading study abroad consultancy, helping students secure university admissions in the UK, USA, Canada, EU, and UAE. We are expanding and opening a new branch in Calicut, and we’re looking for passionate and dynamic Senior International Student Counsellors to join our team.</p><p><br></p><p>Apply now and help students turn their dreams into reality!</p>', '<p></p><ul><li>Be part of a fast-growing international education company.</li><li>Work in a supportive and interactive environment.</li><li>Network with top universities and students worldwide.</li><li>Competitive salary, incentives, and career growth opportunities.</li></ul><p></p><p><br></p>', '<p></p><ul><li>Guide students on study opportunities, applications, and visa processes.</li><li>Promote top global universities to potential students.</li><li>Manage student applications and records in the CRM.</li><li>Build strong relationships with students and partner institutions.</li><li>Collaborate with the marketing team to create engaging promotional content.</li></ul><p></p>', '<p></p><ul><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Minimum 1 years of experience in study abroad counselling.</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; A Bachelor’s degree (Business or IT background preferred).</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Excellent communication and persuasion skills.</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Strong customer service and problem-solving abilities.</li><li>&nbsp; &nbsp; Confidence, resilience, and a goal-oriented mindset.</li></ul><p></p><p><br></p>', 'International Student Counsellor', '1', 'AIMS Education', 'First Floor, City corner complex, West Nadakkave, Vandipetta, Bilathikkulam, Kozhikode, Kerala 673011, India', 'https://aimseducation.co.uk', 1, 1, '2025-07-16 03:42:37', '2025-07-21 12:15:12'),
(70, 'Web Designer', 'web-designer', 9, 6, 3, 1, NULL, '01 December, 2025', 'Dhaka, Bangladesh', '<p>We are seeking a Web Designer Intern to join our dynamic team. The ideal candidate will be responsible for creating visually stunning website designs and engaging content for our website that aligns with our brand and helps communicate our message effectively to our audience.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Skills Required:</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Proficiency in Figma</li><li>Knowledge of HTML and CSS</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Work Environment:</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>This is an in-office position</li><li>Office hours are from 9 AM to 5 PM</li></ul><p><strong><br></strong></p><p><strong>How to Apply:</strong></p><p>&nbsp;If you meet the above criteria and are excited about gaining hands-on experience in web design, please send your CV and a cover letter.</p><p></p>', NULL, '<p></p><ul><li>Perform data entry tasks</li><li>Work on designing projects using Figma</li></ul><p></p>', '<p></p><ul><li>B.Sc./Diploma in CSE</li><li>Minimum CGPA of 3.5 or equivalent</li></ul><p></p>', 'Web Designer', '1', 'AIMS Education', 'Islam Tower, 102, Sukrabad Mirpur Rd, Dhanmondi, Dhaka-1207, Bangladesh', 'https://aimseducation.co.uk', 0, 1, '2025-07-16 03:53:14', '2025-07-21 12:14:45'),
(71, 'Sale Executive', 'sale-executive', 10, 1, 3, 10, NULL, '01 December, 2025', 'Sylhet, Chattogram', '<p>A well-reputed educational and education support organisation named; AIMS Academy, AIMS English and AIMS Education. We have over 130+ people working in a number of positions in Bangladesh. We offer an excellent salary, Provident Fund, Top Up and bonus package along with a work-life balance job. Currently, we are looking for Sale Executive to sell our courses for AIMS Academy and AIMS English for both Sylhet and Chattogram Branches.</p><p><strong>Skills Required:&nbsp;</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Computer, Counseling, Good commend in English and IELTS Score could be preferred.</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Experience Requirements</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Candidate must have experience at least 1 year(s)</li><li>The applicants should have experience in the following business area(s):</li><li>Immigration &amp; Education Consultancy Service</li></ul><p><br></p><p><strong>Additional Requirements</strong></p><p></p><p></p><ul><li>Age 20 to 35 years</li><li>Highly dedicated and challenge taking.</li><li>Presentable, self-motivated and target oriented approach.</li><li>Ability to establish &amp; maintain good rapport with students.</li><li>Ability to communicate effectively with students of all ages and social background.</li><li>Apply Procedure</li></ul><p></p>', '<p></p><ul><li>Compensation &amp; Other Benefits</li><li>Provident Fund</li><li>Company Top-Up</li><li>Commission on Student recruitment</li><li>Incentive on target fill up (Yearly)</li><li>2 Festival Bonuses</li><li>Mobile and Mobile bill, Tour allowance, Performance bonus</li></ul><p></p>', '<p></p><ul><li>Excellent communication skills</li><li>Education Counseling and Sales</li><li>Students profile assessment</li><li>Partner communications</li><li>Counseling local &amp; international students directly, over phone &amp; social media.</li><li>Email communication.</li><li>Outsourcing</li><li>Can Operate CRM online activity.</li><li>Had to do other official tasks which are given by Management.</li></ul><p></p>', '<p></p><ul><li>Master and Bachelor degree in any discipline.</li></ul><p></p>', 'Sale Executive', '1', 'AIMS Academy and AIMS English', 'ABC Point, Uposhahar, Sylhet, Bangladesh', 'https://www.aims-academy.com', 0, 1, '2025-07-16 04:02:53', '2025-07-21 12:13:54'),
(72, 'International Student Recruitment Officer', 'international-student-recruitment-officer', 1, 1, 3, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Southend-on-Sea', '<p><strong>Skills Requirements:</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Can persuade and influence, gain leverage over others, persistent, resilient, and confident in their ability to close deals.</li><li>Provide first-class customer service.</li><li>Excellent communication, interpersonal, problem-solving, presentation, and organisational skills.</li><li>Proven success rate at levels above quotas and sales goals.</li><li>Must be computer literate</li><li>Education Background:</li></ul><p></p><p><br></p><p><strong>Language Requirements:</strong></p><p></p><ul><li>Fluent in English.</li></ul><p><br></p><p></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Ideal candidate can be offered Skilled Worker Visa</span></p>', NULL, '<p></p><ul><li>Advise students on study opportunities in the UK, Canada, and Australia.</li><li>Advise students on the application and visa application procedures and guide the student through all processes until enrolment is complete.</li><li>Market and promote educational institutions represented by the company to students.</li><li>Maintain an accurate ledger of student details and applications in the CRM system.</li><li>Liaise with university students, other offices, and client institutions.</li><li>Create and build relationships with university students.</li><li>Create personal marketing strategies to engage clients.</li><li>Complete accurate administrative tasks for the role.</li><li>&nbsp;<strong>The Candidate:</strong></li></ul><p></p><p>Our ideal candidate will be a real people person, have a positive, can-do attitude and the willingness to achieve and succeed in their work. A background in student recruitment is not necessary as full training will be provided. The ideal candidate will be customer-focused and driven to meet and exceed targets.</p>', '<p>An undergraduate degree from any reputable University. An applicant from a Business, Marketing, English or IT background will be preferable.</p>', 'International Student Recruitment Officer', '1', 'AIMS Education', 'Princess Caroline House (Ground Floor), 1 High St, Southend-on-Sea SS1 1JE, United Kingdom', 'https://aimseducation.co.uk', 0, 0, '2025-07-16 04:20:27', '2025-07-16 04:44:21'),
(73, 'Brand Ambassador', 'brand-ambassador', 2, 4, 3, 20, NULL, '22 December, 2025', 'Anywhere', '<p>We seek some outgoing and enthusiastic individual, who is passionate about our brand and can effectively communicate our message to the public.</p><p>As a brand ambassador, you will represent our company and promote our services to potential clients. Your role is crucial in building brand awareness and loyalty, increasing sales and creating a positive image for our company.</p><p>In this position, you will have the opportunity to use your creativity and networking skills to create a strong brand presence across various channels, including social media, events and community outreach programs.</p><p>If you are a natural communicator who enjoys building relationships and has a keen eye for marketing, we encourage you to apply for this exciting opportunity.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>Start Date:</strong> Immediate Start</p><p><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Voluntary</p><p><strong>Salary: </strong>Commission/incentive base</p>', NULL, '<p></p><ul><li>Representing the company at various events and functions</li><li>Establishing and maintaining business relationships with the audience, especially at school, colleges and Universities.</li><li>Building up marketing campaigns, ideating content and responding to posts that will build up a community of followers.</li><li>Collaborating with the marketing team to develop new strategies for increasing brand awareness and sales.</li><li>Required Skills and qualifications</li><li>Student at degree or master level or recently completed</li><li>Strong understanding of marketing principles and techniques.</li><li>Vast Knowledge and experience with using social media and other marketing channels.</li><li>Able to create social media content</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Ability to build and maintain relationships with customers and industry professionals.</li></ul><p></p>', NULL, 'Brand Ambassador', '1', 'AIMS Education', 'Princess Caroline House (Ground Floor), 1 High St, Southend-on-Sea SS1 1JE, United Kingdom', 'https://aimseducation.co.uk', 1, 1, '2025-07-16 04:43:56', '2025-07-21 11:18:36');

